1
00:00:00,000 --> 00:00:06,383
Why does it feel like everyone else is living chapter twenty while you're stuck in chapter three?

2
00:00:06,383 --> 00:00:12,014
The quiet panic says you're already behind — that you should be further by now.

3
00:00:12,014 --> 00:00:23,653
Charles Darwin formed his theory of natural selection in 1838. He did not publish On the Origin of Species until 1859 — more than twenty years of evidence, revision, and restraint.

4
00:00:23,653 --> 00:00:25,906
What looked like delay was construction.

5
00:00:25,906 --> 00:00:34,166
Today, stop measuring your unfinished foundation against someone else's finished house. Do one honest hour of the work only you can do.

6
00:00:34,166 --> 00:00:37,920
You are not behind in life. You are being built.
